                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/10250" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">STR-2587</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">285 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">承一人之志，启众行之远：纽绅集团三十年发展背后的企业家精神</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">From Individual Aspiration to Collective Advancement: The Entrepreneurial Spirit Behind the 30-Year Development of New Century Group</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">丰超，高莹莹，张译心，许苏南，陈慧（通讯作者），陈怿，向泓，李丽，毛灿</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">南京航空航天大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">贵州纽绅教育发展有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">服务业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">小微型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">15 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">民办教育；企业家精神；组织管理；教育创新；社会责任</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Private Education; Entrepreneurial Spirit; Organizational Management; Education innovation; Social responsibility</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本案例围绕纽绅教育集团三十年发展历程中的关键人物——创始人项宏，剖析其企业家精神如何贯穿于企业的创业、成长与高质量发展各阶段。案例从1996年创办贵阳首家少儿英语培训学校写起，展现了项宏如何在政策不确定、资源有限的背景下，以教育理想为引领推动教学方法革新、实现初步市场突破。随着业务拓展，纽绅面临组织协同、人才流失、政策冲击等多重挑战。案例深入描绘了她通过“统一管理、分散经营”的组织治理模式，设立临时工作机制，构建教师梯队与数字化赋能系统等举措，持续推动组织转型与创新升级。通过项宏的个人视角与关键管理事件，本案例展现了教育行业创业者如何在复杂环境中实现从“个人使命”到“组织能力”的跃迁。本案例适用于企业战略管理、组织行为学等教学主题，并可引导学生围绕企业家精神的阶段性演化、组织变革实践与社会责任议题展开深入讨论。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">This case focuses on Xiang Hong, the founder and key figure behind the 30-year development of N-Century Group, analyzing how her entrepreneurial spirit runs through the enterprise&#39;s startup, growth, and high-quality development stages. Beginning with the establishment of Guiyang&#39;s first children&#39;s English training school in 1996, the case demonstrates how Xiang Hong led teaching method innovations and achieved initial market breakthroughs guided by educational ideals against the backdrop of policy uncertainties and limited resources. As the business expanded, N-Century Group faced multiple challenges such as organizational coordination, talent drain, and policy shocks. The case deeply depicts her continuous promotion of organizational transformation and innovative upgrading through measures including the &quot;centralized management with decentralized operation&quot; governance model, the establishment of temporary work mechanisms, and the construction of teacher echelons and digital empowerment systems. Through Xiang Hong&#39;s personal perspective and key management events, this case illustrates how entrepreneurs in the education industry achieve the transition from &quot;personal mission&quot; to &quot;organizational capability&quot; in complex environments. It is suitable for teaching topics such as corporate strategic management and organizational behavior, and can guide students to conduct in-depth discussions on the phased evolution of entrepreneurial spirit, organizational change practices, and social responsibility issues.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《企业战略管理》、《组织行为学》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">企业家精神；组织学习理论；企业文化</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-12</td>
